race.description: The Lids Fly On Ladbrokes Live Channels
race.comment: SEE THIS (4) has hit the frame at six of 16 starts and has won two of last three, the latest scoring (29.98) over 520m at this track. Solid record at the distance winning four races. Rates highly here and will go close. RED ROCK RAZZLE (8) has a strong record this journey here with two wins and a minor from five starts. Scored by a nose last time (30.10) in a Grade 4/5 over 520m at this track. Looks suited here and can measure up. OVERFLOW JENNY (2) finished fifth last time but the start prior broke the clock when winning over 400m at Bulli, taking a Grade 5 in a dominant 22.35. Top win two back and rates a key player again. ROSACKY RAYO (1) will give backers a sight.
